name: Interstellar Incorporated: Monopolize the Galaxy!
blurb: Explore new systems, mine resources, manufacture goods to satisfy consumer demands, manage your trading fleet, monopolize the galaxy!

rewards.reward: "MINER" LEVEL: YOUR OWN GAME COPY + BETA ACCESS! - A digital DRM-free download plus game key of the full version of the game for PC or Mac (or Steam download voucher/key if preferred) upon product release. For backing this project now you will also be granted access to the beta test program shortly before game launch.

"REFINER" LEVEL: ALPHA ACCESS! - All previous rewards plus exclusive high-res screensavers of 12 pieces of fine artwork from the game. You will also be given automatic access to the earliest alpha version of the game, allowing you to provide input and influence the later development stages so that it becomes the best scifi business simulation this side of Andromeda.
"PILOT" LEVEL: BRANDED T-SHIRT! - All previous rewards plus exclusive branded t-shirt in your size.
"HARBOURMASTER" LEVEL: BRANDED GOODIES PACKAGE! - All previous rewards plus exclusive branded accessories kit including pen, mug and mousemat.

"MANUFACTURER" LEVEL: BRANDED GOODIES AND ART-BOOK PACKAGE! - All previous rewards plus softcover coffee-table book of artwork, sketches, project photos of the game's development signed by the leading team members.

"COLONIST" LEVEL: YOUR OWN ROCK + CONTRIBUTOR CREDIT! - All previous rewards plus have an in-game non-terrestrial world named after you. This will appear in-game as "[Your Last Name]'s Rock". Where duplicate last names exist, your initial or first name will also be added in keeping with appropriate content and style. Receive a "Contributor" game credit.

"MANAGER" LEVEL: YOUR OWN STAR SYSTEM + CONTRIBUTOR CREDIT! - All previous rewards plus have an in-game star system named after you. This will appear in-game as "[Your Last Name]'s Star/System". Where duplicate last names exist, your initial or first name will also be added in keeping with appropriate content and style. Receive a "Contributor" game credit.

"DIRECTOR" LEVEL: YOUR OWN TERRESTRIAL WORLD + SPONSOR CREDIT! - All previous rewards plus have an in-game Earth-classed (fully habitable) world named after you. This will appear in-game as "[Your Last Name]'s World". Your other (non-terrestrial) world will be named "_____'s Rock" Where duplicate last names exist, your initial or first name will also be added in keeping with appropriate content and style. Receive a "Sponsor" game credit.

"GOVERNOR" LEVEL: YOUR OWN RESEARCH BREAKTHROUGH + PATRON CREDIT! - All previous rewards plus have a research technology dedicated to you! Such a mention would link the research technology to your name, such as "[Your Last Name]'s Effect" or "Breakthroughs in [Technology] by [Your Last Name]". Receive a "Patron" game credit.

"CHIEF EXEC" LEVEL: MEET THE TEAM + HONOURED PATRON CREDIT! All previous rewards plus spend an afternoon and evening, including dinner, with the leading members of the team, gaining an exclusive insight into the development process, and inadvertently our personal habits. Includes the cost of dinner, but does not include travel or accomodation expenses. Receive a "Patron" game credit.

"TYCOON" LEVEL: BE THE FACE OF ONE OF THE TEN TYCOONS + EXEC PRODUCER CREDIT! All previous rewards up to \u00a3250 plus have your face as one of the ten playable tycoons in the game. An appropriately taken photo of you would be used as the basis for one of the ten tycoon's portraits which will feature prominently throughout the game. Choice of tycoon slots are awarded on a  priority basis to those first pledging. Adjustments will be made to conform your portrait to in-game styling and any racial characteristics to the target tycoon. Receive an "Executive Producer" game credit.
